{
  "id": "RAW_1ff075",
  "title": "Gemini 2.5：性能提升，模型迎来重大更新",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/gemini-25-our-world-leading-model-is-getting-even-better/",
  "date": "2025-05-20 17:45:10",
  "author": "Tulsee Doshi",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-05-20T17:45:10.563581+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$896463105$--><span width=\"14px\">\n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg></span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable> <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7varr\" class=\"drop-cap\">In March, we announced <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/google-deepmind/gemini-model-thinking-updates-march-2025/?utm_source=deepmind.google&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=gdm&amp;utm_content=\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/google-deepmind/gemini-model-thinking-updates-march-2025/?utm_source=deepmind.google&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=gdm&amp;utm_content=&quot;}\">Gemini 2.5 Pro</a>, our most intelligent model yet, and two weeks ago, we brought you our<a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-2-5-pro-updates/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-2-5-pro-updates/&quot;}\"> I/O update early</a> for developers to build incredible web apps. Today, we’re sharing even more updates to our <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/?_gl=1*1hcx28i*_up*MQ..*_ga*OTE5NDY4NDk5LjE3NDc1NzI2Mzk.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc1NzI2MzgkbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc1NzI2MzgkajAkbDAkaDA.\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/?_gl=1*1hcx28i*_up*MQ..*_ga*OTE5NDY4NDk5LjE3NDc1NzI2Mzk.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc1NzI2MzgkbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc1NzI2MzgkajAkbDAkaDA.&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini 2.5</a> model series:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"52qlu\">Beyond 2.5 Pro’s incredible performance <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/pro/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/pro/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">on academic benchmarks</a>, it’s now the world-leading model across the <a href=\"https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WebDev Arena</a> and <a href=\"https://lmarena.ai/?leaderboard\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://lmarena.ai/?leaderboard&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">LMArena</a> leaderboards, and for <a href=\"https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/education/google-gemini-learnlm-update\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/education/google-gemini-learnlm-update&quot;}\">helping people learn</a>.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"41s5v\">We’re bringing new capabilities to 2.5 Pro and 2.5 Flash: native audio output for a more natural conversational experience, advanced security safeguards, and <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/project-mariner/?_gl=1*1c8pzpn*_up*MQ..*_ga*MTg3MDY5NzA5LjE3NDc0MTgwOTc.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc0MTgwOTckbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc0MTgxMDAkajAkbDAkaDA.\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/project-mariner/?_gl=1*1c8pzpn*_up*MQ..*_ga*MTg3MDY5NzA5LjE3NDc0MTgwOTc.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc0MTgwOTckbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc0MTgxMDAkajAkbDAkaDA.&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Project Mariner</a>’s computer use capabilities. 2.5 Pro will get even better with <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/gemini/pro\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/models/gemini/pro&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Deep Think</a>, an experimental, enhanced reasoning mode for highly-complex math and coding.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ba9vd\">We continue to invest in the developer experience, introducing thought summaries in the <a href=\"https://www.googleadservices.com/pagead/aclk?sa=L&amp;ai=DChcSEwisvpPlh62NAxVhkVAGHQQyExAYABABGgJkZw&amp;co=1&amp;ase=2&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwiqbBBhCAARIsAJSfZkb2UNm71aDTiQj43uE6u_X4kdQjkW-zJE4ys1-WPCsHAjQPW0JsAfEaAnO5EALw_wcB&amp;ohost=www.google.com&amp;cid=CAESVuD2XZH0cGUhnUN_hgWfLPh0qxdkyaxfS7GgJW3CE1EWqyyuEGeFtJxpp-RPP_6lGT_tcrNml8Z0ycbys16CbucweCE9iTf9Fezie1FFOvssm7ZxarUX&amp;category=acrcp_v1_5&amp;sig=AOD64_3P3Z7aCoP-AB8jidfzdFepXVjQQg&amp;q&amp;nis=4&amp;adurl&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjz0Y7lh62NAxXXSEEAHTUKO98Q0Qx6BAgKEAE\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://www.googleadservices.com/pagead/aclk?sa=L&amp;ai=DChcSEwisvpPlh62NAxVhkVAGHQQyExAYABABGgJkZw&amp;co=1&amp;ase=2&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwiqbBBhCAARIsAJSfZkb2UNm71aDTiQj43uE6u_X4kdQjkW-zJE4ys1-WPCsHAjQPW0JsAfEaAnO5EALw_wcB&amp;ohost=www.google.com&amp;cid=CAESVuD2XZH0cGUhnUN_hgWfLPh0qxdkyaxfS7GgJW3CE1EWqyyuEGeFtJxpp-RPP_6lGT_tcrNml8Z0ycbys16CbucweCE9iTf9Fezie1FFOvssm7ZxarUX&amp;category=acrcp_v1_5&amp;sig=AOD64_3P3Z7aCoP-AB8jidfzdFepXVjQQg&amp;q&amp;nis=4&amp;adurl&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjz0Y7lh62NAxXXSEEAHTUKO98Q0Qx6BAgKEAE&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a> and in <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a> for more transparency, extending thinking budgets to 2.5 Pro for more control, and adding support for MCP tools in the Gemini API and <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/migrate\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/migrate&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SDK</a> for access to more open source tools.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"5ht49\">2.5 Flash is now available to everyone in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://gemini.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a>, and we'll make our updated version generally available in <a href=\"http://aistudio.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://aistudio.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a> for developers and in <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a> for enterprises in early June, with 2.5 Pro soon after.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6ogjt\">This remarkable progress is the result of the relentless effort of teams across Google to improve our technologies, and develop and release them safely and responsibly. Let’s dive in.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7varr\">2.5 Pro performs better than ever</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2q0i8\">We recently <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-2-5-pro-updates/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-2-5-pro-updates/&quot;}\">updated 2.5 Pro</a> to help developers build richer, interactive web apps. It’s great to see the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c6UkBTTOIAE%27\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c6UkBTTOIAE%27&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">positive reaction from users and developers</a> and we’re continuing to make improvements based on user feedback.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"98pb5\">In addition to its strong performance on academic benchmarks, the new 2.5 Pro is now leading the popular coding leaderboard, <a href=\"https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WebDev Arena</a>, with an ELO score of 1415. It’s also leading across all leaderboards of the <a href=\"https://lmarena.ai/?leaderboard\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://lmarena.ai/?leaderboard&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">LMArena</a>, which evaluates human preference in various dimensions. And, with its 1 million-token context window, 2.5 Pro has state-of-the-art <a href=\"https://developers.googleblog.com/en/gemini-2-5-video-understanding/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://developers.googleblog.com/en/gemini-2-5-video-understanding/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">long context and video understanding performance</a>.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5d28d\">Since incorporating LearnLM, our family of models built with educational experts, 2.5 Pro is also now the <a href=\"https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/education/google-gemini-learnlm-update\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/education/google-gemini-learnlm-update&quot;}\">leading model for learning</a>. In head-to-head comparisons evaluating its pedagogy and effectiveness, educators and experts preferred Gemini 2.5 Pro over other models across a diverse range of scenarios. And, it <a href=\"https://goo.gle/LearnLM-May25\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://goo.gle/LearnLM-May25&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">outperformed top models</a> on every one of the <a href=\"http://goo.gle/learnlm\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://goo.gle/learnlm&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">five principles of learning science</a> used to build AI systems for learning.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7msn9\">Read more in our updated <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/model-cards/documents/gemini-2.5-pro-preview.pdf\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/model-cards/documents/gemini-2.5-pro-preview.pdf&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini 2.5 Pro model card</a> and on the <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini technology page</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"7varr\">Deep Think</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"98mqg\">Through exploring the frontiers of Gemini’s thinking capabilities, we’re starting to test an enhanced reasoning mode called <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/gemini/pro\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/models/gemini/pro&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Deep Think</a> that uses new research techniques enabling the model to consider multiple hypotheses before responding.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9j0sl\">2.5 Pro Deep Think gets an impressive score on <a href=\"https://maa.org/news/2025-usamo-and-usajmo-thresholds-now-available/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://maa.org/news/2025-usamo-and-usajmo-thresholds-now-available/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2025 USAMO</a>, currently one of the hardest math benchmarks. It also leads on <a href=\"https://livecodebench.github.io/leaderboard.html\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://livecodebench.github.io/leaderboard.html&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">LiveCodeBench</a>, a difficult benchmark for competition-level coding, and scores 84.0% on <a href=\"https://mmmu-benchmark.github.io/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://mmmu-benchmark.github.io/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MMMU</a>, which tests multimodal reasoning.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Chart demonstrating Gemini 2.5 Pro Deep think's advanced capabilities\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better\" external-link=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/deep-think-chart.original.jpg\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Inline Images&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n        }\">\n    <!--?lit$896463105$--><a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/deep-think-chart.original.jpg\" alt=\"Chart demonstrating Gemini 2.5 Pro Deep think's advanced capabilities\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$896463105$-->\n     <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n      <!--?lit$896463105$-->\n      <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n       <img alt=\"Chart demonstrating Gemini 2.5 Pro Deep think's advanced capabilities\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/deep-think-chart.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/deep-think-chart.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/deep-think-chart.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n      </div><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?--> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?--> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?-->\n     </div></a> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7varr\">Because we're defining the frontier with 2.5 Pro DeepThink, we're taking extra time to conduct more frontier safety evaluations and get further input from safety experts. As part of that, we’re going to make it available to trusted testers via the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a> to get their feedback before making it widely available.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7varr\">An even better 2.5 Flash</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"dvqoj\"><a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2.5 Flash</a> is our most efficient workhorse model designed for speed and low-cost — and it’s now better across many dimensions. It’s improved across key benchmarks for reasoning, multimodality, code and long context while getting even more efficient, using 20-30% less tokens in our evaluations.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Chart comparing Gemini 2.5 Flash with other models\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better\" external-link=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_2-5_flashcomp_benchmarks_cropped_light2x.gif\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Inline Images&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n        }\">\n    <!--?lit$896463105$--><a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_2-5_flashcomp_benchmarks_cropped_light2x.gif\" alt=\"Chart comparing Gemini 2.5 Flash with other models\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$896463105$-->\n     <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n      <!--?lit$896463105$-->\n      <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n       <img alt=\"Chart comparing Gemini 2.5 Flash with other models\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_2-5_flashcomp_benchmarks_cropped_light2x.gif\">\n      </div><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?--> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?--> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?-->\n     </div></a> <!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?lit$896463105$--><!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7varr\">The new 2.5 Flash is now available for preview in <a href=\"http://aistudio.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://aistudio.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a> for developers, in <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/studio/multimodal?model=gemini-2.5-flash-preview-05-20\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/studio/multimodal?model=gemini-2.5-flash-preview-05-20&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a> for enterprise and in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://gemini.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a> for everyone. And in early June, it’ll be generally available for production.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5r2e7\">Read more in our updated <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/model-cards/documents/gemini-2.5-flash-preview.pdf\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/model-cards/documents/gemini-2.5-flash-preview.pdf&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini 2.5 Flash model card</a> and on the <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini technology page</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7varr\">New Gemini 2.5 capabilities</h2>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"d9bl\">Native audio output and improvements to Live API</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4evov\">Today, the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/live\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/live&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Live API</a> is introducing a preview version of audio-visual input and native audio out dialogue, so you can directly build conversational experiences, with a more natural and expressive Gemini.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"d3bfb\">It also allows the user to steer its tone, accent and style of speaking. For example, you can tell the model to use a dramatic voice when telling a story. And it supports tool use, to be able to search on your behalf.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2c5pb\">You can experiment with a set of early features, including:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"e56oe\">Affective Dialogue, in which the model detects emotion in the user's voice and responds appropriately.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"8qc0a\">Proactive Audio, in which the model will ignore background conversations and know when to respond.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"90h2p\">Thinking in the Live API, in which the model leverages Gemini’s thinking capabilities to support more complex tasks.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"a7sud\">We’re also releasing new previews for text-to-speech in 2.5 Pro and 2.5 Flash. These have first-of-its-kind support for multiple speakers, enabling text-to-speech with two voices via native audio out.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7sdii\">Like Native Audio dialogue, text-to-speech is expressive, and can capture really subtle nuances, such as whispers. It works in over 24 languages and seamlessly switches between them.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-youtube-player-article index=\"14\" thumbnail-alt=\"Native audio output example\" video-id=\"n3LPxbVzVeo\" video-type=\"video\" image=\"Native Audio Outputs\" video-image-url-lazy=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nativ.width-100.format-webp.webp\" video-image-url-mobile=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nativ.width-700.format-webp.webp\" video-image-url-desktop=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nati.width-1000.format-webp.webp\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Youtube Video&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"n3LPxbVzVeo\" data-index-id=\"14\" data-type=\"video\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n      <a role=\"video\" class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nativ.width-100.format-webp.webp\" alt=\"Native audio output example\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nati.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/thumbnail_16-9_EnablingDevs_Nativ.width-700.format-webp.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250514-1654#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250514-1654#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><!--?lit$896463105$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component iconid=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250514-1654#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"7varr\">This text-to-speech capability will be available later today in the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"9e5ln\">Computer use</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7eavv\">We're bringing <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/project-mariner/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/project-mariner/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Project Mariner</a>'s computer use capabilities into the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a> and <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>. Companies like Automation Anywhere, UiPath, Browserbase, Autotab, The Interaction Company and Cartwheel are exploring its potential, and we're excited to roll it out more broadly for developers to experiment with this summer.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"9e5ln\">Better security</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"ek2gi\">We’ve also significantly increased protections against security threats, like indirect prompt injections. This is when malicious instructions are embedded into the data an AI model retrieves. Our <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/Security%20and%20Privacy/Gemini_Security_Paper.pdf\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/Security%20and%20Privacy/Gemini_Security_Paper.pdf&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">new security approach</a> helped significantly increase Gemini’s protection rate against indirect prompt injection attacks during tool use, making Gemini 2.5 our most secure model family to date.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"1ku92\">Read more about <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/about/responsibility-safety/?_gl=1*10qw615*_up*MQ..*_ga*NDcyMjA1ODA3LjE3NDc0MDI5ODA.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc0MDI5ODAkbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc0MDI5ODAkajAkbDAkaDA.\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/about/responsibility-safety/?_gl=1*10qw615*_up*MQ..*_ga*NDcyMjA1ODA3LjE3NDc0MDI5ODA.*_ga_LS8HVHCNQ0*czE3NDc0MDI5ODAkbzEkZzAkdDE3NDc0MDI5ODAkajAkbDAkaDA.&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">our work across safety, responsibility and security</a>, and <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/advancing-geminis-security-safeguards/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/advancing-geminis-security-safeguards/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">how we’re advancing Gemini’s security safeguards</a> on the Google DeepMind blog.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"9e5ln\">Enhanced developer experience</h2>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"3hio0\">Thought summaries</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"a76vk\">2.5 Pro and Flash will now include thought summaries in the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a> and in <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>. Thought summaries take the model’s raw thoughts and organize them into a clear format with headers, key details and information about model actions, like when they use tools.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9h2em\">We hope that with a more structured, streamlined format on the model’s thinking process, developers and users will find the interactions with Gemini models easier to understand and debug.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"9e5ln\">Thinking budgets</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"804j6\">We launched 2.5 Flash with thinking budgets to give developers more control over cost by balancing latency and quality. And we’re extending this capability to 2.5 Pro. This allows you to control the number of tokens a model uses to think before it responds, or even turn its thinking capabilities off.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"fstq0\">Gemini 2.5 Pro with budgets will be generally available for stable production use in the coming weeks, along with our generally available model.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2.5: Our most intelligent models are getting even better&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"9e5ln\">MCP support</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"a9n3t\">We added native SDK support for Model Context Protocol (MCP) definitions in the Gemini API for easier integration with open-source tools. We’re also exploring ways to deploy MCP servers and other hosted tools, making it easier for you to build agentic applications.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bml2p\">We’re always innovating on new approaches to improve our models and our developer experience, including making them more efficient and performant, and continuing to respond to developer feedback, so please keep it coming! We also continue to double down on the breadth and depth of our fundamental research — pushing the frontiers of Gemini’s capabilities. More to come soon.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"e5hdh\">Learn more about <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/#introduction&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini and its capabilities on our website</a>.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-related-content-tout title=\"I/O 2025\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"We’re doing cutting-edge research to build the most helpful AI that’s more intelligent, agentic and personalized.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Collection\" image-alt-text=\"Stylized 3D text &quot;IO25&quot; in vibrant, gradient colors on a white grid background.\" role=\"none\" fullurl=\"https://blog.google/technology/developers/google-io-2025-collection/\" pagetype=\"collectiondetailpage\" isarticlepage=\"\">\n   <!---->\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Google 宣布对 Gemini 2.5 Pro 和 Flash 模型进行重大更新，包括增强推理能力、原生音频功能、计算机使用能力以及开发者工具。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 宣布对 Gemini 2.5 Pro 和 Flash 模型进行重大更新，包括增强推理能力、原生音频功能、计算机使用能力以及开发者工具。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了 Google Gemini 2.5 模型系列的最新进展，重点介绍了 Pro 和 Flash 版本。主要更新包括在编码 (WebDev Arena)、人类偏好评估 (LMArena) 和教育学习（整合 LearnLM）等方面取得世界领先的性能。文章还介绍了一种新的实验性 'Deep Think' 模式，该模式适用于 2.5 Pro，并在复杂数学 (USAMO) 和编码 (LiveCodeBench， MMMU) 任务中展示了卓越的推理能力。Gemini 2.5 Pro 和 Flash 模型都获得了用于自然对话的原生音频输出，并通过 API 集成了 'Project Mariner' 以实现计算机使用能力。2.5 Flash 现在效率更高，评估中使用的 token 减少了 20-30%，同时提高了基准测试的性能。此外，Gemini 2.5 显著提升了针对间接提示注入的安全性，使其成为迄今为止最安全的模型系列。通过思维总结提高透明度，可控的思维预算以及改进的 SDK 对开源工具的支持，从而增强了开发者体验。这些功能正在推广到 Google AI Studio、Vertex AI 和 Gemini 应用程序。",
